text: CF Ungheni (also named FC Ungheni) is a Moldovan football club from Ungheni. The club was founded in 2012CF Ungheni vrea să joace în Divizia Naţională! Clubul a depus actele la Federaţia Moldovenească de Fotbal, publika.md and currently plays in the Divizia A, the second tier of Moldovan football. ==Achievements== *Divizia B : Winners (1): 2014–15 ==References== ==External links== * *Profile at Soccerway *Profile at divizia-a.md *Profile at Facebook Category:Football clubs in Moldova Category:Association football clubs established in 2012 Category:Moldovan "A" Division
